Synonyms</st>
<p>

The Soda Apple has been described under a range of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../296/8166296.xml">
junior synonym</link>s, now invalid. Several of these are ambiguous <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../126/148126.xml">
homonym</link>s:<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref>
